     fhir:text [ fhir:v "I switched from Dexcom G6 CGM to Abbott Freestyle Libre 3+ in November 2024, but still use Dexcom occasionally. I find Dexcom sensors to be more accurate. Libre tends to show lower readings for me, compared to fingerstick measurements (with all glucometers I've tried)." ]
